Don't wear yerself out yet, Minime, the votes arn't over! And members can 
always change their vote!

::Ramulus::

A bit surprised by the reports of the change, Ramulus keeps quiet for a 
moment, trying to figure out how a DNA transplant (or so to speak) occured. 
As far as he knew, the beast mode was part of the protoform, not of the spark.

(Great!), he replies, (Yeah, I think I should go back to my body now, it'd 
feel great to be able to move again!)
